# Add Capture Timestamp to Vision Pipeline

## Goal
統一時間基準：在畫面**擷取時刻**記錄時間戳，並傳遞到整個處理鏈，消除因處理延遲造成的時序偏差。

## Proposed Changes

### 1. LiveViewManager.cs
#### 新增 `TimestampedFrame` record
```csharp
public record TimestampedFrame(Mat Frame, DateTime CaptureTime);
```

#### 修改 [OnCaptureTimer](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/LiveViewManager.cs#136-161)
在擷取成功時記錄時間戳：
```csharp
var captureTime = DateTime.UtcNow;
frameQueue.Enqueue(new TimestampedFrame(frameMat.Clone(), captureTime));
```

#### 修改 `OnFrameReady` 事件
```csharp
public event Action<Mat, DateTime>? OnFrameReady;
```

#### 修改 [OnDetectionTimer](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/LiveViewManager.cs#162-222)
傳遞 [CaptureTime](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/LiveViewManager.cs#136-161) 給訂閱者：
```csharp
OnFrameReady?.Invoke(latestFrame.Frame, latestFrame.CaptureTime);
```

---

### 2. MainForm.cs
#### 修改 `OnFrameReadyHandler`
接收 `captureTime` 並傳遞給 [GameVisionCore](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/GameVisionCore.cs#69-77)：
```csharp
private void OnFrameReadyHandler(Mat frame, DateTime captureTime)
{
    // ...
    var result = _visionCore.GetMinimapTracking(frame, captureTime);
    // ...
}
```

---

### 3. GameVisionCore.cs
#### 修改 [GetMinimapTracking](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/GameVisionCore.cs#259-396) 簽名
```csharp
public MinimapTrackingResult? GetMinimapTracking(Mat fullFrameMat, DateTime captureTime)
```

使用傳入的 `captureTime` 而非 `DateTime.UtcNow`。

---

### 4. RouteRecorderService.cs
不需修改。它已經從 `MinimapTrackingResult.Timestamp` 讀取時間。

---

## Verification
1. 建置成功
2. 錄製跳躍時，Hook 時間與 Vision 時間直接對齊，無需延遲補償
